"{\"uid\": \"flotrack.org-articles-12770178-2024-olympic-updates-results-aug-8-am-can-the-us-get-the-stick-around\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Adidas Indoor Nationals  Texas Distance Festival  Chandler Rotary Invite  W&L Outdoor T&F Carnival  Run Rome the Marathon  David Noble Relays  Emory Thrills in the Hills  WashU Distance Carnival  Jim Taylor Duals  Doc Jopson Invitational  2026 FSU Relays  Continental Tour: Maurie Plant Meet  WashU Invite  Monmouth Home Opener  Corsair Classic  Day 7 ofOlympic track and field actiongot underway at the Stade de France on Thursday morning, featuring the opening of the women's heptathlon, men's and women's 4x100m heats, women's shot put qualification, and repechage rounds in the women's 100mH and men's 800m.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 123, \"end\": 134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_F._Noble\", \"score\": 0.9999999997089617, \"rank\": 1.9134324325675205e-10, \"text\": \"David Noble\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_F._Noble\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_F._Noble\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yesterday's evening session featured finals in the men's 400m, 3000m steeplechase, and discus plus women's pole vault finals.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Several more final and semifinal fields will be set in the qualifying rounds this session.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This morning, five qualifying events will be contested, consisting of repechage \\\"second chance\\\" rounds in the women's 100mH and men's 800m, as well as the first rounds of the women's shot put and both 4x100m relays.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 1046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside those events, the two-day women's heptathlon will begin featuring American Anna Hall.\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1123, \"end\": 1131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"score\": 0.6108982980291954, \"rank\": 0.636933494777661, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Hall_Roosevelt\", \"score\": 0.9999999736746762, \"rank\": 2.6325111930959233e-08, \"text\": \"Anna Hall\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Hall_Roosevelt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Hall_Roosevelt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay tuned for live updates across the morning session.\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Only the winner of each of 4 heats will auto-qualify for the semis, plus the next two fastest losers.\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Heat 1  After a 53.1 opening split, Botswana's 1:43 manKethoboglie Hainhuraholds on to win the first heat in 1:45.52.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999983714328283, \"rank\": 1.6285700451625385e-06, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Back in 6th, Dennick Luke sets a new national record for Dominica in 1:46.81.)\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9999803090123918, \"rank\": 1.875899369665955e-05, \"text\": \"Luke\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Spencer\"}, {\"begin\": 1480, \"end\